				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$R\bar3m$$\end{document} symmetry product, which in turn is unable to achieve a high capacity as obtained from the C2/m distorted structure.
